{"tid":1681324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商人涉 3,000 元毒品賄賂警員 警員疑曾於被告住所吸毒 控方未決定會否拘控","createTime":"2019-10-29T10:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T10:56:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b81d273fa71021b0b2b238074aedb3e0bf90ec9f","tid":1681324,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"男商人被指串謀販運毒品及以總值 3,000 元的毒品賄賂一名警員，遭廉署控以一項串謀販毒及 3 項向公職人員提供利益罪，案件今於西九龍裁判法院提堂，被告暫毋須答辯，押後 12 月 13 日再訊並獲准保釋。據了解，涉案警員王得嘉疑曾於被告的住所內服食可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n控方則於庭外表示，暫時未有指示是否會拘捕及控告涉案警員。據了解，被告於在 2017 年 8 月中至 9 月中期間，先後 3 次接受警員王得嘉及其他警務人員會見以提供情報，其後被告兩次以折扣價向警員王得嘉提供可卡因，其中一次王得嘉更於被告住所內服食可卡因，被告另曾免費向王得嘉提供 1 克可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n被告王偉明（59歲），被控 3 項向公職人員提供利益罪及一項串謀販運危險藥物罪。控罪指他於 2017 年 8 月 1 日至 12 月 31 日期間，無合法權限或合理辯解，兩次以折扣價向警員王得嘉提供可卡因，及在另一場合向對方免費提供約 1 克可卡因，涉案可卡因總值 3,000 元，作為使王得嘉傾向或保持傾向優待被告的誘因或報酬。被告另被控一項串謀販運危險藥物罪名，指他於同一時期，與其他不知名者串謀非法販運可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89-3-000-%E5%85%83%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E8%B3%84%E8%B3%82%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E6%9B%BE%E6%96%BC%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8E%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589-3-000-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25B3%2584%25E8%25B3%2582%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%2590%25B8%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=da465335\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589-3-000-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25B3%2584%25E8%25B3%2582%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%2590%25B8%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&h=019ccccc\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89-3-000-%E5%85%83%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E8%B3%84%E8%B3%82%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E6%9B%BE%E6%96%BC%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8E%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"16e52525fd22115d38f95c5707226b701cf08c77","tid":1681324,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a7aa3312b3c0a8bb255f57e8ca441e1deb629cb9","tid":1681324,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"仆街死黑警 知法犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7ee21404563a9961cca223169a24048b24adfc","tid":1681324,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"告佢正契弟，千其咪撚告呀"},{"pid":"f710734b440158d91db213ba5759435b9a90c638","tid":1681324,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"[榮光歸港人互助計劃] 讓有需要既手足都能以成本價買野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681328</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論